RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

99-910. State ex rel. Schrichten v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 98AP-170. Reported at 90 Ohio St.3d 436, 739 N.E.2d 331. On amicus curiae motion for leave to file under S.Ct.Prac.R. XI by the Ohio AFL-CIO and on motion for reconsideration. Motions denied.

Douglas, Resnick and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent.
